data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled on 3.5 acres. As you enter the main house boasting 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and an inviting living room adorned with gleaming hardwood floors. Host unforgettable dinners in the formal dining room or enjoy cozy meals in the spacious eat-in kitchen, complete with stainless steel appliances including a refrigerator. Relax and unwind in the sunroom, basking in the warmth of natural light streaming through the windows. A convenient laundry room/ mud room make chores become a breeze. There is a tong and groove floored attic upstairs! But that's not all - this property offers versatility with an in-law suite designed in a studio layout, featuring a stylish bathroom with a tiled shower. Outside, discover the detached oversized workshop and garage, providing ample space for hobbies, storage, or tinkering on projects.
